<h1>Topbar and Navigation playground</h1>
<p>A layout prototype for testing combinations of topbar and navigation variants — exploring structure, hierarchy, and focus order in a controlled environment.</p>

<h2>How to use</h2>
<p>Use the options panel to switch between different topbar and navigation types. Not all combinations are valid — some navigation types only work with specific topbar types.</p>

<h2>Known limitations</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Some layout combinations are still visually experimental</li>
    <li>Focus order and accessibility behavior may need further research / development</li>
    <li>Styles are not polished and intended only for testing</li>
    <li>Some features are not fully implemented (e.g., language selector, ...)</li>
</ul>
